VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT RAILS_ENV\s*=\s*[\'\"]development[\'\"]|config\.consider_all_requests_local\s*=\s*true
WHEN EXPR MISSING:release|production
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects development/debug settings in deployable Ruby app configs.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Sinatra Development/Debug Mode Enabled.
